data.description: This well maintained home is perfect for the large family. Located in a quiet neighborhood, the newer home offers everything you would want minutes from the beautiful Black Hills. The kitchen features semi custom cabinets with granite in both the kitchen and baths. With a large 3 car garage, 6 bedrooms, multi outdoor patio areas and a hot tub that stays, this is a perfect sanctuary. The main suite has an impressive walk in closet and a semi custom walk in shower. The lower level is completely finished with 3 bedrooms, a huge family room, and a secret bunker room for storm safety or storing gun safes etc.  Hot tub has been drained and winterized. Priced at low sq footage per sq ft.  Check it out.
